Instead of installing system libraries on Jenkins, you can run your pipeline inside a Node container:

pipeline {
    agent {
        docker {
            image 'node:20'
        }
    }
    stages {
        stage('Install') {
            steps {
                sh 'npm install'
            }
        }
    }
}